### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7101
@orderId = {{CreateOrder.response.body.data.orderId}}

### 1. Get Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary

### 2. Get Dashboard Summary for Specific Month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary?month=2025-09

### 3. Quick Order - با مشتری جدید
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/quick
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newCustomer": {
    "fullName": "مشتری تست سریع",
    "phoneNumber": "09123456789",
    "companyName": "شرکت تست",
    "isTemporary": false
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 1500000
    }
  ],
  "note": "سفارش تستی"
}

### 4. Quick Order - با مشتری موجود
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/quick
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 2500000
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Quick Order - ثبت سفارش به نام کاربر دیگر (فقط Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/quick
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "quantity": 3,
      "unitPrice": 1800000
    }
  ]
}

### 6. Get Sales Monthly Report (6 ماه اخیر)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/monthly?months=6

### 7. Get Sales Monthly Report (سفارشی)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/sales/monthly?months=12&year=2025

### 8. Confirm Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/{{orderId}}/confirm

### 9. Cancel Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/{{orderId}}/cancel

### 10. Get Order Details (برای بررسی وضعیت)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Orders/{{orderId}}

### 11. Complete Dashboard Flow
# 1. دریافت خلاصه داشبورد
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary

###
